---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Contact Us - TaxPortal" description="Contact TaxPortal for inquiries, feedback, or suggestions.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Contact Us</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
          <p>We value your feedback and inquiries. Whether you have a question, suggestion, or need assistance, please reach out to us.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>For general inquiries, feedback, or suggestions about TaxPortal, please contact us through the following channels:</p>
          
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">Email</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">support@taxportal.com</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Feedback</h2>
          <p>We welcome your suggestions for new calculators, countries, or features. Your input helps us improve TaxPortal for everyone.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Send a Message</h2>
          <form class="space-y-4" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
            <p class="hidden" aria-hidden="true"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
            <div>
              <label for="contact-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-1 dark:text-on-primary">Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required class="w-full rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas px-4 py-2 text-ink focus:border-primary focus:outline-none dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:text-on-primary" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="contact-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-1 dark:text-on-primary">Email</label>
              <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" required class="w-full rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas px-4 py-2 text-ink focus:border-primary focus:outline-none dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:text-on-primary" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="contact-subject" class="block text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-1 dark:text-on-primary">Subject</label>
              <input type="text" id="contact-subject" name="subject" required class="w-full rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas px-4 py-2 text-ink focus:border-primary focus:outline-none dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:text-on-primary" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="contact-message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-1 dark:text-on-primary">Message</label>
              <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="4" required class="w-full rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas px-4 py-2 text-ink focus:border-primary focus:outline-none dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:text-on-primary"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-primary-dark dark:bg-on-primary dark:text-primary">Send Message</button>
          </form>
          
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Partnerships</h2>
<p>If you are interested in partnering with TaxPortal or have business inquiries, please reach out with your proposal. You can also learn more about our mission on the <a href="/about" class="text-link hover:underline dark:text-link">About</a> page.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Quick Links</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/countries" class="text-link hover:underline dark:text-link">Browse Country Tax Information</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blogs" class="text-link hover:underline dark:text-link">Read Tax Blog Articles</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="text-link hover:underline dark:text-link">Learn About TaxPortal</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
